name: QrArtWarningKind
summary: Warning kinds for QR art safety evaluation.

fields.name: QuietZoneTooSmall
fields.summary: Quiet zone is below the recommended size (4 modules).

fields.name: ModuleSizeTooSmall
fields.summary: Module size is too small for reliable scanning.

fields.name: LowContrast
fields.summary: Contrast between foreground and background is too low.

fields.name: LowContrastGradient
fields.summary: Gradient includes colors with low contrast against the background.

fields.name: LowContrastPalette
fields.summary: Palette includes colors with low contrast against the background.

fields.name: ModuleScaleTooSmall
fields.summary: Module scale is too small (excessive rounding or shrink).

fields.name: FunctionalPatternsUnprotected
fields.summary: Functional patterns are not protected while decorative styling is enabled.

fields.name: QuietZonePatterned
fields.summary: Background pattern may be drawn into the quiet zone.

fields.name: LogoTooLarge
fields.summary: Logo covers too much of the QR area.

fields.name: LogoNeedsHighEcc
fields.summary: Logo is used with low error correction.
